statements: SELECT * FROM quantum_algorithms
SELECT algorithm_name, description FROM quantum_algorithms
SELECT algorithm_id, algorithm_name FROM quantum_algorithms WHERE algorithm_id = 1
SELECT * FROM quantum_algorithms ORDER BY algorithm_name DESC
SELECT algorithm_name, description FROM quantum_algorithms WHERE parallelization_strategy = 'Primary'
SELECT * FROM quantum_algorithms ORDER BY algorithm_id DESC;
SELECT algorithm_name, description FROM quantum_algorithms WHERE parallelization_strategy = 'Quantum Annealing';
SELECT algorithm_id, algorithm_name FROM quantum_algorithms WHERE algorithm_id > 3 ORDER BY algorithm_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM quantum_algorithms WHERE description LIKE '%quantum%' AND algorithm_name LIKE '%Grover%';
SELECT algorithm_name, parallelization_strategy FROM quantum_algorithms WHERE algorithm_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT * FROM Quantum_Algorithms;
SELECT algorithm_name, parallelization_level FROM Quantum_Algorithms;
SELECT * FROM Algorithm_Implementations WHERE implementation_id = 1;
SELECT algorithm_name, implementation_name FROM Quantum_Algorithms, Algorithm_Implementations WHERE Quantum_Algorithms.algorithm_id = Algorithm_Implementations.algorithm_id;
SELECT implementation_name, parallelization_support FROM Algorithm_Implementations WHERE algorithm_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM Quantum_Algorithms;
SELECT algorithm_id, algorithm_name, parallelization_level FROM Quantum_Algorithms WHERE parallelization_level > 5;
SELECT implementation_name, parallelization_support FROM Algorithm_Implementations WHERE algorithm_id = 2 ORDER BY implementation_name ASC;
SELECT algorithm_name, implementation_name FROM Quantum_Algorithms JOIN Algorithm_Implementations ON Quantum_Algorithms.algorithm_id = Algorithm_Implementations.algorithm_id;
SELECT * FROM Quantum_Algorithms WHERE algorithm_name LIKE 'Q%';
SELECT * FROM QuantumAlgorithms;
SELECT algorithm_name, parallelization_level FROM QuantumAlgorithms ORDER BY algorithm_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM QuantumComputers WHERE qubits_count > 10;
SELECT brand, used_qubits, available_qubits FROM QuantumComputers WHERE used_qubits < available_qubits ORDER BY brand;

SELECT a.algorithm_name, c.brand, ap.parallelization_status FROM QuantumAlgorithms a JOIN AlgorithmParallelization ap ON a.algorithm_id = ap.algorithm_id JOIN QuantumComputers c ON ap.computer_id = c.computer_id;
SELECT * FROM QuantumAlgorithms;
SELECT algorithm_name, parallelization_level FROM QuantumAlgorithms WHERE parallelization_level > 5;
SELECT brand, qubits_count, used_qubits FROM QuantumComputers ORDER BY qubits_count DESC;

SELECT algorithm_name, brand, parallelization_status FROM QuantumAlgorithms JOIN AlgorithmParallelization ON QuantumAlgorithms.algorithm_id = AlgorithmParallelization.algorithm_id JOIN QuantumComputers ON AlgorithmParallelization.computer_id = QuantumComputers.computer_id;

SELECT algorithm_name, parallelization_level, brand, qubits_count FROM QuantumAlgorithms JOIN AlgorithmParallelization ON QuantumAlgorithms.algorithm_id = AlgorithmParallelization.algorithm_id JOIN QuantumComputers ON AlgorithmParallelization.computer_id = QuantumComputers.computer_id WHERE parallelization_level <= 3 AND qubits_count >= 50;
SELECT * FROM QuantumComputers;
SELECT id, brand, model FROM QuantumComputers WHERE qubits_count > 50;
SELECT * FROM QuantumCircuits ORDER BY num_gates DESC;
SELECT id, description FROM QuantumCircuits WHERE id BETWEEN 10 AND 20;
SELECT task_name, completed FROM QuantumTasks WHERE created_at < '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, brand, model FROM QuantumComputers WHERE qubits_count > 50;
SELECT * FROM QuantumCircuits WHERE num_gates >= 100 ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT task_name, completed FROM QuantumTasks WHERE completed = false ORDER BY created_at ASC;
SELECT gate_name, gate_type FROM QuantumGateLibrary WHERE id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT id, name, description, num_gates FROM QuantumCircuits WHERE name LIKE '%Quantum%' OR description LIKE '%algorithm%' LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM quantum_algorithms;
SELECT task_id, task_name FROM quantum_tasks WHERE algorithm_id = 1;
SELECT worker_name, task_name, result_data FROM quantum_workers INNER JOIN quantum_tasks ON quantum_workers.task_id = quantum_tasks.task_id;
SELECT task_name, error_message FROM quantum_tasks INNER JOIN quantum_errors ON quantum_tasks.task_id = quantum_errors.task_id WHERE quantum_tasks.task_id = 3;
SELECT algorithm_name, MAX(parallelization_level) AS max_parallelization FROM quantum_algorithms;
SELECT * FROM quantum_algorithms;
SELECT task_name, algorithm_name FROM quantum_tasks INNER JOIN quantum_algorithms ON quantum_tasks.algorithm_id = quantum_algorithms.algorithm_id;
SELECT worker_name, result_data FROM quantum_workers INNER JOIN quantum_results ON quantum_workers.task_id = quantum_results.task_id;
SELECT algorithm_name, COUNT(task_id) FROM quantum_algorithms LEFT JOIN quantum_tasks ON quantum_algorithms.algorithm_id = quantum_tasks.algorithm_id GROUP BY algorithm_name;
SELECT task_id, task_name, error_message FROM quantum_tasks LEFT JOIN quantum_errors ON quantum_tasks.task_id = quantum_errors.task_id WHERE error_id IS NOT NULL ORDER BY task_id DESC;
